## 🆔 Auto ID Generation

Submission IDs are generated automatically:
```java
private static String generateSubmissionId() {
    return "SUB-" + (++submissionCounter);
}
```
- Counter starts at `2000`, so first ID is `SUB-2001`
- IDs are distinct from Challenge IDs (`CHG-`) for easy identification in logs

