## 🏗 How SubmissionService Fits in the Architecture

```
Developer
  └── calls submitSolution()
                │
                ▼
        SubmissionService  ◄── platform submission registry
               │
               ├── validates content
               ├── checks for duplicates
               ├── creates Submission object
               ├── registers in allSubmissions list
               ├── calls Challenge.addSubmission()
               └── calls Developer.trackSubmission()
                              │
                              ▼
                      EvaluationService
                      (picks up PENDING submissions for scoring)
```

